<br>
I'm not legally or morally bound into saying &quot;WTG Reso&quot; at the drop of a hat. If I wanted to, I could, and I'm sure I'd fit right in with the other people doing it. What a guild does for hours on end is none of my concern, and thus, I don't care about it.<br>
<br>
Perhaps it is you that should examine your attitude towards this. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ujharycleric.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jharycleric</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 225<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/13/02 10:59:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1193.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: How bout someone saying- Congratulations</span><hr size=1> Because we have a section called Kudos for it. This is the Soapbox, where we BITCH about stuff. <br>
<br>
Jhary<br>
Iksatr Cleric<br>
Prophetic Alliance<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umistressoftherose.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mistress of the Rose</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Black Rose</span><br>  Posts: 393<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/13/02 11:23:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1193.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://noirdaila.homestead.com/files/ZDoll.JPG width=83 height=154></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: How bout someone saying- Congratulations</span><hr size=1> Raiding is &quot;NOT&quot; only about getting loot.<br>
<br>
I give a rats ass about loot but recently I applied and was accepted into Fire and Fury.  Challenge is one of the biggest reasons I applied.<br>
<br>
That is why you will hardly ever see me in Velketor's Labryinth.  It's not a challenge (well besides when I get to pull doggies and gargies) but you get the point.  Seb is likewise boring as is Fungus Grove.  So normally the only place that I ask to go is Cazic Thule ... and not the zoneline because I feel that is easy also.<br>
<br>
For me the challenge of fighting big mobs is a lot of fun.  I also do tradeskills and also get around to roleplay with people .... so what is with the assumption that everyone in one of these guilds is just in it for loot? <p><B>Zsuzsana Dracul</B><BR><I>Beguiler of the 59th Jewel</I><BR>
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=205913">Quit Staring at Me.  Here is a picture.<BR><LEFT><img src="http://www.fireandfury.org/sigs/Zsuzsana.jpg"></A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uscarfase.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Scarfase</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/13/02 11:24:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1193.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: How bout someone saying- Congratulations</span><hr size=1> I think you have all missed the point. Go to Kudos and look. You will not find the congrats to these Guilds.<br>
<br>
I am not saying everyone must mindlessly praise them. I am saying in light of all the complaining I would hope that people could congratulate them as well.<br>
<br>
It seems that the rule here is that if you have nothing good to say then please say it.<br>
<br>
I personally find this dissapointing.<br>
<br>
Exxy <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utzarothfv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tzaroth FV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 101<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/13/02 11:39:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1193.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: How bout someone saying- Congratulations</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Raiding is &quot;NOT&quot; only about getting loot.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
I disagree with this statement, but my only question has to do with why the word <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> not</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> is in quotations.<br>
<br>
